         <tr> 
          <td style="width: 25%" class="auto-style1" valign="top"><strong>CONTACT HOURS</strong></td> 
          <td style="width: 75%" class="auto-style1">190</td> 
         </tr> 
         <tr> 
          <td style="width: 25%" class="auto-style1" valign="top"><strong>CONTENT</strong></td> 
          <td style="width: 75%" class="auto-style1">This NEW program will consist of various lectures and practical evolutions to meet the competencies for certification in the State of New Jersey and Pro Board Certification. This course will meet the N.F.P.A. 1001 standard for level I certification. This course is designed to instruct the students on the subjects / modules required for Fire Fighter I certification. Attending students will be required to pass a Pro-Board written examination, and tested on all practical skills to receive their accreditation. </td> 
         </tr> 
